# Platform Admin

## Routes (5 pages)

- `/admin/dashboard` — platform overview + analytics insights
- `/admin/organizations`
- `/admin/subscriptions`
- `/admin/users`
- `/admin/settings`

## Theme

- **Light theme** — same palette as public/dashboard (`bg-background`, `bg-card`, `border-border`, `text-primary`).
- **No dark sidebar.** Sidebar uses `bg-card`, active link `bg-feature-sync text-primary`.
- **Roboto** in admin layout only (`font-roboto` on admin shell + Ant Design `fontFamily`).

## Layout

- `AdminLayout`: sidebar + header + `<Outlet />`
- Desktop (≥880px / `nav:`): fixed sidebar
- Mobile: sidebar hidden; hamburger opens Ant Design `Drawer`
- Logout: red primary danger button → `ConfirmModal` → clear user → `/login`

## Admin pages pattern

1. Page header (title, description, primary action)
2. Stat cards from `src/data/admin-*.ts`
3. Table with toolbar (search, filter, bulk actions)
4. Use shared `Table` + `TablePaginationFooter`

## Bulk delete pattern

- Disabled until ≥1 row selected
- Label shows count when selected: `Bulk Delete (3)`
- Confirm via `ConfirmModal` before applying

## Roles (future reference)

Signup → **Organization Owner**. Platform Admin is separate (FlowSync owner). V1 roles: Platform Admin, Organization Owner, Admin, Manager, Member.
